projectMetadata.name: PunkScapes
projectMetadata.description:
10k little landscapes that punks can inhabit – on the Ethereum Blockchain.

[OneDayPunks](https://opensea.io/collection/onedaypunks) and [CryptoPunks](https://larvalabs.com/cryptopunks) get an [ENS](https://ens.domains/) powered profile on punkscape.xyz.

Everyone else can rock them on their socials... Roadmap in Discord.

projectMetadata.name: One Day Punks
projectMetadata.description: 10k 'One Day I'll Be A Punk' punks – a homage to the one and only CryptoPunks.

projectMetadata.name: Skulptuur (ArtBlocks)
projectMetadata.description: An exploration in generating forms in 3-dimensional space. This exclusive set of sculptures has been carved from a sea of infinite possibilities, much like a sculptor creates a singular reality from the potential in a block of stone. The shapes are illuminated by a variety of complex virtual lighting environments and yet the piece retains algorithmic minimalism with the code reduced to its pure essence -- 6370 bytes. Skulptuurs render in real time. In live view, the image keeps improving in quality. Keys 0-7 change speed: 0=Stop, 5=Default, 7=Fastest. Careful, requires a powerful machine. Requires a WebGL2-enabled browser.

projectMetadata.name: Bored Ape Yacht Club
projectMetadata.description: The Bored Ape Yacht Club is a collection of 10,000 unique Bored Ape NFTs— unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain...

projectMetadata.name: doodles
projectMetadata.description: A community-driven collectibles project featuring art by Burnt Toast. Doodles come in a joyful range of colors, traits and sizes with a collection size of 10,000. Each Doodle allows its owner to vote for experiences and activations paid for by the Doodles Community Treasury.
